quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  82,1,Si kammu on fettii
  82,2,Si koode ɗe cariima
  82,3,Si maaje ɗe puccitaama
  82,4,Si genaale mbaylaama
  82,5,Fittaandu annda kondu waɗno e golle e kondu leelnuno e golle
  82,6,Eehey ma neɗɗanke hol ko hoomtuma e joom ma Tedduɓɗo O
  82,7,Oon takɗo ma O fotndi terɗ ma O waɗ ma potandirɗo
  82,8,E kala mbaadi ndi O haaja O feewnir ma
  82,9,"Alah, woni ko on yeddooɓe ñalngu noɓdi"
  82,10,Pellet ina woodi e dow mon malaykaaji deenooji
  82,11,Tedduɗi binndooji
  82,12,Gannduɗi ko ngolloton
  82,13,Pellet ɓeen ɗigguɓe hoɓe e neema
  82,14,Faajireeɓe noon ina e yiite
  82,15,Hoɓe naatange ñande ñalngu njoɓdi
  82,16,ɓe ngonah wirnatooɓe nge haa bada
  82,17,Holko anndin ma ñalngu njobdi
  82,18,Refti holko anndin ma ñalngu njobdi
  82,19,ñande fittaandu jogantaaki fittaandu hay huunde huunde fof ko Alla woodani ñande heen